# Types of Regression

## Linear Regression

Assumes a linear relationship between variables.

Most commonly used regression algorithm.

---

## Polynomial Regression

Used when relationships are curved rather than straight.

---

## Multiple Linear Regression

Uses multiple input variables.

Example:

Age + BMI + Children + Smoker

↓

Insurance Charges

