# Evaluation Metrics

## MAE

Mean Absolute Error

Average prediction error.

---

## MSE

Mean Squared Error

Squares prediction errors.

---

## RMSE

Root Mean Squared Error

Measures prediction accuracy.

---

## R² Score

Measures how much variation the model explains.

Range:

0 to 1

Higher is better.

